1
00:00:00,440 --> 00:00:01,430
[Disclaimer:
All depicted events are fictional

2
00:00:01,460 --> 00:00:02,460
and for entertainment purposes only;
viewer discretion is advised]

3
00:00:14,540 --> 00:00:18,540
[Love Upon a Time Series]

4
00:00:18,560 --> 00:00:20,700
Should we converge upon
the designated hour and place,

5
00:00:20,720 --> 00:00:22,180
we shall undoubtedly capture Cherd.

6
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:23,770
Should we manage to capture him,

7
00:00:23,800 --> 00:00:26,520
we might be able to use him to
trace back to the one who framed my father.

8
00:00:26,550 --> 00:00:27,010
Phop!

9
00:00:27,040 --> 00:00:29,960
Tell me everything that you know
about my father.

10
00:00:31,910 --> 00:00:33,420
You already know, do you not?

11
00:00:33,980 --> 00:00:35,880
I must accompany Father to Phichit.

12
00:00:36,330 --> 00:00:38,120
I do not wish to be parted from you.

13
00:00:38,220 --> 00:00:42,220
[Phichit]

14
00:00:46,090 --> 00:00:47,790
We are officials of the state,

15
00:00:48,230 --> 00:00:50,850
entrusted with the duty
of safeguarding the welfare of the people.

16
00:00:51,440 --> 00:00:54,560
Having been granted a life far more bountiful
than that of the common folk,

17
00:00:54,900 --> 00:00:56,400
we cannot commit such an act.

18
00:00:57,830 --> 00:00:59,300
I shall accept only your kindness.

19
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,670
As for all else,

20
00:01:02,170 --> 00:01:03,680
I must most respectfully decline.

21
00:01:47,240 --> 00:01:48,050
Who might that be?

22
00:01:48,750 --> 00:01:49,610
I know not, Master.

23
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,720
I only gather that
he is a nobleman from the capital.

24
00:01:58,910 --> 00:01:59,680
Father.

25
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:01,160
Father.

26
00:02:07,680 --> 00:02:08,919
Has something occurred?

27
00:02:10,419 --> 00:02:12,870
There is nothing for you
to trouble your heart over, son.

28
00:02:13,350 --> 00:02:14,960
I have already settled the matter.

29
00:02:17,590 --> 00:02:18,220
Son,

30
00:02:18,760 --> 00:02:20,720
you have been studying and writing all day.

31
00:02:21,940 --> 00:02:22,760
Are you weary?

32
00:02:24,160 --> 00:02:24,910
I am,

33
00:02:25,630 --> 00:02:26,980
yet I do so with all my heart.

34
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:30,600
Perhaps, when the day comes
that I become an official,

35
00:02:31,070 --> 00:02:32,820
I may ease the burden upon your shoulders.

36
00:02:34,900 --> 00:02:36,120
My deepest thanks, son.

37
00:02:37,860 --> 00:02:39,760
I entrust
the greatest hopes of our future to you.

38
00:02:41,290 --> 00:02:41,920
Yes, Father.

39
00:02:43,340 --> 00:02:44,520
But if it is too wearisome,

40
00:02:44,670 --> 00:02:45,520
on the morrow

41
00:02:46,060 --> 00:02:47,500
shall we venture to the market?

42
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:48,340
A splendid idea, my Lord.

43
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:51,000
Chuay.

44
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:52,840
It appears you are eager to

45
00:02:52,890 --> 00:02:54,680
accompany my son on this outing.

46
00:02:55,650 --> 00:02:56,520
If that be the case,

47
00:02:56,930 --> 00:02:59,180
how about you set forth
and wait for us at the market tonight?

48
00:03:00,130 --> 00:03:00,880
Wonderful idea, my Lord.

49
00:03:01,500 --> 00:03:02,400
I shall take my leave now.

50
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:10,730
The hour is far too late.

51
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,240
Look at him.

52
00:03:14,800 --> 00:03:15,560
Chuay.

53
00:03:16,380 --> 00:03:17,680
Are you so eager to set forth?

54
00:03:18,300 --> 00:03:19,079
Very well, onward.

55
00:03:19,790 --> 00:03:20,520
Let us depart.

56
00:03:20,829 --> 00:03:22,440
We shall set out at this hour.

57
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,380
Come.

58
00:03:23,440 --> 00:03:24,360
Master Klao.

59
00:03:24,540 --> 00:03:25,450
- Now.
- Master!

60
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:27,370
Chuay, do take good care of my son,
will you?

61
00:03:27,390 --> 00:03:28,079
Yes, my Lord!

62
00:03:49,950 --> 00:03:51,800
Father, can you truly not tell me...

63
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:53,420
when you shall return?

64
00:03:56,590 --> 00:03:59,180
High Lord Pichayabhakdi
has given no word regarding my return.

65
00:04:00,630 --> 00:04:02,020
But I believe it shall be brief.

66
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:05,460
His Excellency likely requires my aid
in matters of tongue

67
00:04:05,980 --> 00:04:07,440
to interrogate and examine

68
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:10,040
the Chinese and the Farangi merchants

69
00:04:10,950 --> 00:04:12,440
regarding the smuggling of opium.

70
00:04:13,010 --> 00:04:14,450
Remain here and await my return.

71
00:04:16,850 --> 00:04:17,490
But...

72
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,730
I wish to accompany you.

73
00:04:20,720 --> 00:04:22,029
I wish to see Phop.

74
00:04:30,070 --> 00:04:32,100
Endure this bitter patience
for a sweeter reward.

75
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:38,159
Once the examination is concluded,

76
00:04:39,340 --> 00:04:41,390
I shall escort you back to the capital.

77
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:57,800
Forgive me, son,

78
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,480
for leaving you to endure such solitude.

79
00:05:04,790 --> 00:05:06,400
I pray this mission

80
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:10,180
shall reach a swift and successful end.

81
00:05:14,170 --> 00:05:16,270
Should His Excellency
look upon our services with favor,

82
00:05:18,340 --> 00:05:19,680
I shall petition for

83
00:05:20,830 --> 00:05:22,610
my reassignment to the capital,

84
00:05:30,540 --> 00:05:32,960
and you shall no longer need to be
so far from your brother.

85
00:05:38,670 --> 00:05:39,320
Yes, Father.

86
00:06:20,450 --> 00:06:21,220
How peculiar.

87
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:25,260
Those fluent in the tongues of
the Chinese and the Farangi

88
00:06:25,830 --> 00:06:27,180
are plentiful in the capital.

89
00:06:28,070 --> 00:06:29,920
Why, then, must they require my father?

90
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:44,720
What did you say?

91
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:48,760
The Lord has been apprehended

92
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:50,280
for assisting Chinese merchants

93
00:06:50,310 --> 00:06:51,400
in smuggling opium.

94
00:06:55,460 --> 00:06:56,440
It cannot be.

95
00:06:57,550 --> 00:06:58,770
My father is a man of the utmost integrity.

96
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:02,760
It is certain that he has been framed.

97
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:04,960
Chuay.

98
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:07,120
Gather my belongings.

99
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,040
We shall depart this very instant.

100
00:07:09,300 --> 00:07:09,880
Yes, Master.

101
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:19,000
The said vessel had illicitly conveyed

102
00:07:19,360 --> 00:07:22,160
a vast quantity of opium into the kingdom.

103
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:25,480
Furthermore, a warrant was discovered

104
00:07:25,700 --> 00:07:29,210
permitting the vessel
to pass through the river's mouth

105
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,920
without being searched.

106
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,850
Lord Preechapiban.

107
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:49,360
Will you confess to your misdeeds?

108
00:07:51,530 --> 00:07:53,720
The Legal Principles decree that

109
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:58,200
whosoever is found guilty of bribery,

110
00:07:58,720 --> 00:08:00,280
or of engaging in corruption,

111
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,830
such as the trafficking of opium,

112
00:08:04,200 --> 00:08:08,900
shall receive fifty lashes
upon the back,

113
00:08:09,430 --> 00:08:11,600
be subjected to a fourfold fine,

114
00:08:11,940 --> 00:08:15,000
and condemned to a life of servitude.

115
00:08:16,340 --> 00:08:17,340
Father!

116
00:08:54,440 --> 00:08:56,440
[Love Upon a Time Series]

117
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:10,000
[Love Upon a Time Series]

118
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:15,920
Memories of my father are back.

119
00:10:16,690 --> 00:10:18,000
It went much like what Phop told me,

120
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:19,920
but one thing is bugging me.

121
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:23,800
That sword.

122
00:10:24,810 --> 00:10:26,040
Where have I seen it before?

123
00:10:41,650 --> 00:10:42,540
Phop.

124
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:46,520
Kindly partake of a little sustenance.

125
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,360
Dear Klao.

126
00:11:29,760 --> 00:11:30,480
Phop.

127
00:11:31,820 --> 00:11:33,240
If you have no appetite,

128
00:11:33,790 --> 00:11:35,220
at least partake of the meal
to keep me company.

129
00:12:33,310 --> 00:12:35,240
Without you,
how shall I endure this existence?

130
00:13:05,130 --> 00:13:05,880
Dear Klao.

131
00:13:09,300 --> 00:13:10,280
Come with me.

132
00:13:18,510 --> 00:13:20,880
I must now take my leave, Aunt.

133
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:53,010
Good heavens!

134
00:13:53,500 --> 00:13:55,560
When Master Klao disappeared,

135
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:58,080
Lord Phop's physical condition
declined greatly.

136
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:01,200
Should they be separated once more,

137
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,800
I fear that his heart will break
and he will perish.

138
00:14:05,060 --> 00:14:06,100
You speak truly.

139
00:14:21,710 --> 00:14:22,550
Dear Klao.

140
00:14:24,570 --> 00:14:26,890
I have secured for you
a position in the official service of Lavo.

141
00:14:28,230 --> 00:14:30,130
Gather your belongings
and depart on the morrow.

142
00:14:36,300 --> 00:14:38,380
I offer my deepest gratitude,
Your Excellency,

143
00:14:38,580 --> 00:14:39,920
for overseeing this matter on my behalf.

144
00:14:41,920 --> 00:14:42,600
But...

145
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,620
I fear I am unable to depart.

146
00:14:51,290 --> 00:14:52,290
I...

147
00:14:54,290 --> 00:14:56,110
Whatever hardships I might suffer,

148
00:14:56,280 --> 00:14:57,440
I care not.

149
00:14:59,870 --> 00:15:01,330
Yet, if I am no longer by his side,

150
00:15:03,040 --> 00:15:05,120
Phop shall surely perish.

151
00:15:13,260 --> 00:15:14,800
And have you not considered it?

152
00:15:16,940 --> 00:15:18,160
How would you and Phop

153
00:15:19,320 --> 00:15:20,600
live together

154
00:15:21,260 --> 00:15:23,160
without inviting cruel gossip?

155
00:15:28,700 --> 00:15:30,430
I have raised him with the utmost care.

156
00:15:31,950 --> 00:15:34,090
I shall never permit harm to come to him.

157
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:43,060
I ask only to share this heavy burden.

158
00:15:45,440 --> 00:15:48,540
I pray you permit me
to watch over Phop in your stead.

159
00:15:57,400 --> 00:15:58,910
I beg of you.

160
00:16:00,100 --> 00:16:01,870
If you truly look upon me

161
00:16:03,170 --> 00:16:04,430
as one of your own kin,

162
00:16:05,860 --> 00:16:08,630
a child of your dearest friend,
as you once mentioned,

163
00:16:10,020 --> 00:16:12,690
do not force me to part from his side.

164
00:16:20,020 --> 00:16:20,640
Klao!

165
00:16:20,670 --> 00:16:21,320
Depart at once.

166
00:16:21,800 --> 00:16:23,240
Both of us shall set forth.

167
00:16:28,700 --> 00:16:30,120
Should he leave the manor,

168
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:32,600
I too shall depart.

169
00:16:35,800 --> 00:16:38,270
All my life,
I have lived solely for your sake.

170
00:16:41,220 --> 00:16:43,160
I devoted myself to my studies,

171
00:16:44,000 --> 00:16:45,440
and I gave my heart to royal service

172
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:47,400
and to my work in the patrol department,
all for your sake.

173
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:50,270
Even my marriage to Lady Varna,

174
00:16:51,980 --> 00:16:53,440
I dared not refuse

175
00:16:55,640 --> 00:16:57,400
for the deep reverence I bear you.

176
00:17:02,880 --> 00:17:04,150
But from this moment forth,

177
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:08,630
permit me, if only for once,

178
00:17:12,560 --> 00:17:15,010
to follow my own heart for my own sake.

179
00:17:32,760 --> 00:17:33,420
Phop...

180
00:17:33,910 --> 00:17:34,860
Rise, I beg you.

181
00:17:35,060 --> 00:17:36,120
Dear Klao, pray rise.

182
00:17:46,890 --> 00:17:51,280
One cannot simply follow the whims
of one's own heart in every matter, Phop.

183
00:17:52,940 --> 00:17:55,020
Such a path would bring ruin upon your life.

184
00:17:57,120 --> 00:17:58,200
Indeed, Father.

185
00:18:00,790 --> 00:18:02,100
This is my life.

186
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,290
Should ruin come,

187
00:18:08,140 --> 00:18:10,470
let it come by my own hand,

188
00:18:11,450 --> 00:18:13,010
and not by yours, Father.

189
00:18:15,170 --> 00:18:15,960
Phop.

190
00:18:17,050 --> 00:18:18,600
Compose yourself, I beg of you.

191
00:18:23,800 --> 00:18:24,940
My Love,

192
00:18:26,220 --> 00:18:27,860
speak with patience and restraint.

193
00:18:28,530 --> 00:18:31,640
Do not hasten your judgment
while your mind is troubled.

194
00:18:36,710 --> 00:18:37,990
Let it be, Lady Prayong.

195
00:18:41,060 --> 00:18:44,320
I shall no longer render decisions
on Phop's behalf.

196
00:18:52,400 --> 00:18:54,120
Go forth and live your own life.

197
00:18:58,530 --> 00:19:01,040
I shall concern myself
with your affairs no longer.

198
00:19:21,220 --> 00:19:22,480
Phop, what do you...

199
00:19:44,900 --> 00:19:46,510
What do you intend to do?

200
00:19:49,350 --> 00:19:52,040
Surely your father
must be deeply angry with you.

201
00:19:56,590 --> 00:19:59,540
This means that
his heart has already softened.

202
00:20:02,390 --> 00:20:04,960
From this day forth,
no matter what may happen,

203
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:08,520
I shall not let go of your hand.

204
00:20:24,770 --> 00:20:26,030
As a mother,

205
00:20:26,120 --> 00:20:27,120
I am prepared to sacrifice anything.

206
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:30,000
But I cannot bear
to see my child suffer thus, Physician.

207
00:20:30,150 --> 00:20:31,280
Therefore, I implore you

208
00:20:31,330 --> 00:20:32,920
to save my child. I beg of you.

209
00:20:33,000 --> 00:20:34,560
Be that as it may...

210
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:52,440
Do you keep a dog at this manor, Physician?

211
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:55,150
Kaew.

212
00:20:57,700 --> 00:20:58,500
Behold.

213
00:20:58,710 --> 00:21:00,000
It is a dog.

214
00:21:19,200 --> 00:21:20,180
Oh, my!

215
00:21:20,870 --> 00:21:22,440
All sorts of sweets and confections.

216
00:21:22,610 --> 00:21:23,800
They look utterly delectable.

217
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:26,960
Not true. It is merely a ruse
to make me take my remedy.

218
00:21:28,290 --> 00:21:29,600
It is no ruse.

219
00:21:31,910 --> 00:21:32,910
Mm...

220
00:21:34,910 --> 00:21:37,240
Remarkably sweet. It truly is a delight.

221
00:21:37,360 --> 00:21:38,470
Will you not partake with me?

222
00:22:00,710 --> 00:22:01,840
You have my deepest thanks.

223
00:22:11,580 --> 00:22:13,600
Where shall the dog wander?

224
00:22:13,920 --> 00:22:15,680
This way, perhaps?

225
00:22:15,830 --> 00:22:16,880
Can you guess?

226
00:22:16,910 --> 00:22:18,240
Perhaps it is this way?

227
00:22:20,930 --> 00:22:22,040
Or is it this way?

228
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:32,200
Kaew, you are remarkable.

229
00:22:33,160 --> 00:22:35,920
You have soothed my daughter's fear
of the Physician's manor.

230
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,840
Do come back
and play with the dog again, will you?

231
00:22:55,560 --> 00:22:58,440
How did you manage to persuade that child
to take her herbal remedies willingly?

232
00:22:59,300 --> 00:23:00,440
It is quite simple.

233
00:23:00,950 --> 00:23:03,160
I spend my days preparing sweets
day in and day out.

234
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:05,260
Simply by coating your herbal remedies

235
00:23:05,280 --> 00:23:06,440
with honey,

236
00:23:06,480 --> 00:23:07,920
children will find them easier to swallow.

237
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:11,400
I shall remember it.

238
00:23:15,290 --> 00:23:17,240
By seeking me out in this manner,

239
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:19,000
have you truly forgiven me?

240
00:23:19,410 --> 00:23:20,080
No.

241
00:23:20,660 --> 00:23:21,160
However,

242
00:23:22,510 --> 00:23:24,210
Buaphan learned from Chuay that

243
00:23:24,750 --> 00:23:26,430
a grave matter had arisen at Phop's manor.

244
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:28,760
Thus, I have come to urge you to visit Klao.

245
00:23:31,340 --> 00:23:32,560
Go, if you will.

246
00:23:33,830 --> 00:23:35,120
Do as you please.

247
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:49,290
If your heart truly harbors such anger,

248
00:23:50,500 --> 00:23:52,780
why did you come to my manor
seeking me out, Kaew?

249
00:24:02,880 --> 00:24:05,160
It brings me joy to see you smile.

250
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:08,220
Buaphan said that
you had quarreled with His Excellency.

251
00:24:08,250 --> 00:24:09,600
So I thought...

252
00:24:10,460 --> 00:24:11,500
Well...

253
00:24:11,670 --> 00:24:13,400
We did have a quarrel.

254
00:24:14,040 --> 00:24:14,800
But...

255
00:24:15,320 --> 00:24:18,030
when Phop confessed his love
before his father,

256
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:20,080
I knew then that,

257
00:24:20,590 --> 00:24:22,210
no matter the hardships we might face,

258
00:24:22,500 --> 00:24:24,420
we should endure them together.

259
00:24:31,330 --> 00:24:32,960
Since Jom has chosen to accompany you,

260
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:35,120
does this mean

261
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:37,850
you will no longer journey
to Pak Nam Pho, Kaew?

262
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:50,880
Kaew.

263
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,040
I have a matter to discuss with you.

264
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,400
I came here only to see Klao,

265
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:56,620
not to speak with you.

266
00:25:01,970 --> 00:25:03,150
- Klao.
- Hm?

267
00:25:03,320 --> 00:25:04,320
And what of Aunt Bud?

268
00:25:04,630 --> 00:25:06,720
Did she truly bring
the enemy to your doorstep?

269
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:09,380
Uh...

270
00:25:10,920 --> 00:25:12,460
We have no concrete evidence

271
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:14,680
of her conspiring with Cherd.

272
00:25:16,010 --> 00:25:16,840
However...

273
00:25:17,560 --> 00:25:20,300
Aunt had her sent to a small manor.

274
00:25:21,820 --> 00:25:23,200
Once her anger has abated,

275
00:25:23,320 --> 00:25:24,540
she shall return here.

276
00:25:28,950 --> 00:25:29,790
And...

277
00:25:29,880 --> 00:25:31,940
What of the lady at the House of Pleasure?

278
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,590
Knowing how much you love Phop,

279
00:25:35,820 --> 00:25:38,660
I find it hard to believe
you have any affection for that lady,

280
00:25:38,680 --> 00:25:39,840
as rumor has it.

281
00:25:41,210 --> 00:25:43,500
Is there perchance anything
you wish to tell me?

282
00:25:49,600 --> 00:25:50,380
Chuay,

283
00:25:51,450 --> 00:25:52,920
have the servants go down at once.

284
00:25:53,000 --> 00:25:53,680
Yes, my Lord.

285
00:25:54,500 --> 00:25:55,360
Let us leave at once!

286
00:26:09,880 --> 00:26:12,070
So this, then, is the reason
for your visits to the market,

287
00:26:12,110 --> 00:26:13,280
the tavern,

288
00:26:13,660 --> 00:26:14,990
and the House of Pleasure?

289
00:26:16,810 --> 00:26:18,240
Pray, accept my apologies.

290
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:20,160
I misjudged you.

291
00:26:21,490 --> 00:26:22,510
In truth,

292
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:25,040
you came to learn the truth
concerning your father.

293
00:26:26,650 --> 00:26:29,360
And all this while,
you have borne it entirely alone.

294
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:34,620
Forgive me.

295
00:26:35,240 --> 00:26:37,440
At that time, I kept it from you
not because I distrusted you,

296
00:26:38,420 --> 00:26:39,120
but rather...

297
00:26:39,540 --> 00:26:41,100
because I wished to bring
no trouble upon anyone.

298
00:26:48,520 --> 00:26:49,280
Klao.

299
00:26:49,920 --> 00:26:51,850
Henceforth, should any trouble arise,

300
00:26:51,960 --> 00:26:53,760
do not hesitate to speak of it
to Jom and me.

301
00:26:54,540 --> 00:26:55,920
We are willing to help you.

302
00:26:58,380 --> 00:26:59,520
You have my deepest gratitude.

303
00:27:00,620 --> 00:27:02,680
Strangely enough,
I am in need of your assistance.

304
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,240
At this hour,

305
00:27:10,500 --> 00:27:11,800
His Excellency and the lady

306
00:27:12,100 --> 00:27:13,410
are not at the manor.

307
00:27:14,170 --> 00:27:16,640
This gives me the opportunity to
search the quarters.

308
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:19,960
You two must delay the servants

309
00:27:20,460 --> 00:27:22,880
and ensure that
no one sets foot in the manor.

310
00:27:27,320 --> 00:27:28,960
This is no time to set foot in the manor!

311
00:27:29,250 --> 00:27:31,480
Help me search for Dear Kaew's ring at once!

312
00:27:33,860 --> 00:27:34,920
What of that tree?

313
00:27:35,250 --> 00:27:36,750
Do climb up and take a look, will you?

314
00:27:47,960 --> 00:27:48,580
Swords?

315
00:27:48,800 --> 00:27:50,590
It is seldom that
His Excellency is seen bearing his sword.

316
00:27:50,610 --> 00:27:52,240
He looks rather majestic, does he not, Sai?

317
00:27:52,370 --> 00:27:54,880
- Who might that be?
- A nobleman from the capital.

318
00:28:09,200 --> 00:28:09,960
Phop's father...

319
00:28:10,300 --> 00:28:11,420
He killed me?

320
00:28:17,950 --> 00:28:19,330
Being his close friend,

321
00:28:20,100 --> 00:28:21,870
he led my father into opium corruption.

322
00:28:22,540 --> 00:28:23,680
My father refused.

323
00:28:24,250 --> 00:28:25,840
So he framed him?

324
00:28:30,620 --> 00:28:32,720
If he really framed my father,

325
00:28:32,910 --> 00:28:34,730
then taking me into the manor
would only serve

326
00:28:35,390 --> 00:28:37,670
to track everything I do.

327
00:28:38,520 --> 00:28:39,840
This means it is here.

328
00:28:40,200 --> 00:28:41,920
Furthermore, a warrant was discovered

329
00:28:41,980 --> 00:28:44,400
permitting the vessel
to pass through the river's mouth

330
00:28:44,450 --> 00:28:46,080
without being searched.

331
00:28:47,060 --> 00:28:49,800
Is that forged warrant
with my father's fake signature

332
00:28:50,750 --> 00:28:52,110
with Uncle?

333
00:29:01,360 --> 00:29:02,330
Curses!

334
00:29:02,800 --> 00:29:03,680
A key.

335
00:29:04,270 --> 00:29:05,470
A key, a key.

336
00:29:33,300 --> 00:29:34,210
No.

337
00:29:36,530 --> 00:29:37,320
Not this one!

338
00:30:05,260 --> 00:30:09,860
[My dear friend]

339
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:20,320
[You must not come to the capital]

340
00:30:29,870 --> 00:30:30,880
Are you looking for this?

341
00:30:47,330 --> 00:30:48,120
Jom.

342
00:30:48,350 --> 00:30:49,080
Kaew.

343
00:30:49,470 --> 00:30:50,790
Leave the manor for now.

344
00:31:05,320 --> 00:31:06,900
How did that document...

345
00:31:10,740 --> 00:31:13,640
I sent my men to retrieve this evidence
from within the capital.

346
00:31:16,910 --> 00:31:19,240
The handwriting in the letters we exchanged

347
00:31:20,440 --> 00:31:21,500
and this document...

348
00:31:22,390 --> 00:31:25,240
is undoubtedly that of Lord Preechapiban.

349
00:31:26,600 --> 00:31:27,650
See for yourself.

350
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:31,720
Examine it with your own eyes.

351
00:31:33,140 --> 00:31:34,450
The chest is yours to examine.

352
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:03,220
And...

353
00:32:05,100 --> 00:32:06,300
What about those swords?

354
00:32:10,700 --> 00:32:13,600
Any officer of the rank of Lord or higher
is entitled to carry a sword.

355
00:32:15,030 --> 00:32:16,700
Do my swords trouble you in any way?

356
00:32:24,850 --> 00:32:25,640
Uncle...

357
00:32:26,670 --> 00:32:28,120
I ask for your forgiveness.

358
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:34,680
Should you punish him,

359
00:32:36,760 --> 00:32:38,720
punish me as well.

360
00:32:42,040 --> 00:32:43,760
It is my fault for failing to guide him.

361
00:32:49,130 --> 00:32:51,440
I shall not hold this against you.

362
00:32:59,200 --> 00:33:00,820
Take the utmost care of yourself.

363
00:33:04,130 --> 00:33:05,260
As for the case,

364
00:33:06,460 --> 00:33:08,430
I have long been plagued by guilt

365
00:33:09,050 --> 00:33:10,400
for failing to save my dearest friend.

366
00:33:12,370 --> 00:33:13,370
But this time,

367
00:33:14,980 --> 00:33:16,580
I shall be the one to aid you.

368
00:33:22,050 --> 00:33:25,040
I cannot condone your romance with Phop,

369
00:33:29,630 --> 00:33:31,090
yet my affection for you

370
00:33:32,330 --> 00:33:35,170
remains as though you were
my own flesh and blood, as I have always said.

371
00:33:43,370 --> 00:33:46,080
I am profoundly grateful to you,
Your Excellency.

372
00:33:57,360 --> 00:33:59,000
Thank you, Father.

373
00:34:11,449 --> 00:34:13,520
This is all I could do for your son,

374
00:34:14,850 --> 00:34:16,080
Lord Preechapiban,

375
00:34:17,360 --> 00:34:18,400
my dear friend.

376
00:34:22,880 --> 00:34:24,810
The handwriting is indeed identical
in every respect.

377
00:34:26,130 --> 00:34:28,159
Yet my father never smudged ink
upon his writings.

378
00:34:29,010 --> 00:34:31,530
Why, then, is there an ink blot here
and nowhere else?

379
00:34:49,150 --> 00:34:51,080
Why did you enter my father's quarters?

380
00:34:52,000 --> 00:34:53,290
Were you suspicious of him?

381
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:56,420
I...

382
00:34:57,620 --> 00:34:59,160
The sword I saw there

383
00:34:59,610 --> 00:35:01,640
was similar to the one I saw in my dream.

384
00:35:02,750 --> 00:35:04,650
Thus, I suspected him.

385
00:35:05,630 --> 00:35:07,800
I only came to realize that

386
00:35:08,560 --> 00:35:10,720
all the patrolmen carry swords like his.

387
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:15,020
This makes everything more difficult.

388
00:35:15,920 --> 00:35:16,720
No.

389
00:35:17,390 --> 00:35:18,480
Quite the opposite.

390
00:35:19,830 --> 00:35:21,320
Now we know with certainty that

391
00:35:21,730 --> 00:35:23,820
the one who framed your father

392
00:35:25,020 --> 00:35:27,680
must be an officer
of the rank of Lord or higher.

393
00:35:29,200 --> 00:35:31,240
This eliminates a great many
within the capital.

394
00:35:32,980 --> 00:35:33,920
It does indeed.

395
00:35:40,100 --> 00:35:42,810
"The warrant permits the ship from China

396
00:35:43,000 --> 00:35:45,780
to pass through the river's mouth
without being searched."

397
00:35:51,760 --> 00:35:55,230
You were there to see a certain lady

398
00:35:55,250 --> 00:35:58,360
who was accompanied
by a Chinese Port Master.

399
00:36:00,440 --> 00:36:02,680
Do you suspect that Chinese man,
the one with Pim,

400
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:05,840
whom Meng says you quarrelled with?

401
00:36:13,210 --> 00:36:14,320
How could she not be here?

402
00:36:15,240 --> 00:36:16,480
Every time I have come,

403
00:36:16,760 --> 00:36:18,040
Pim has always been here.

404
00:36:19,590 --> 00:36:21,440
She has fallen grievously ill

405
00:36:21,740 --> 00:36:23,840
and has returned to Suvarnabhumi.

406
00:36:24,540 --> 00:36:25,680
Fallen grievously ill?

407
00:36:26,510 --> 00:36:27,510
What ails her?

408
00:36:29,670 --> 00:36:31,640
Perhaps it is a venereal illness.

409
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,920
She will likely be away for a few nights.

410
00:36:35,890 --> 00:36:39,160
Allow Puang to attend to you
in her stead tonight.

411
00:36:45,650 --> 00:36:46,870
It is quite all right.

412
00:36:47,890 --> 00:36:48,830
I shall take my leave.

413
00:36:50,720 --> 00:36:51,900
Master Klao!

414
00:36:52,300 --> 00:36:53,900
Do not leave just now.

415
00:36:54,590 --> 00:36:56,010
I have many tricks, Master.

416
00:36:56,340 --> 00:36:57,600
No charge for this service.

417
00:36:58,920 --> 00:37:00,230
Master Klao!

418
00:37:07,520 --> 00:37:09,390
I went there in vain.

419
00:37:10,290 --> 00:37:12,860
The teahouse was already closed
at that hour.

420
00:37:13,510 --> 00:37:14,990
I am so weary, Phop.

421
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:18,000
Rest if need be.

422
00:37:18,810 --> 00:37:20,040
Would you like to sleep now?

423
00:37:22,530 --> 00:37:24,380
I may find it hard to do so.

424
00:37:25,820 --> 00:37:26,920
Are you feeling sleepy already?

425
00:37:27,790 --> 00:37:30,040
If such is the case,
I shall return to my quarters.

426
00:37:30,990 --> 00:37:32,960
In that case, I fear I cannot find rest,

427
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:35,120
for I shall miss your warmth.

428
00:37:35,450 --> 00:37:37,440
I might shiver myself to death.

429
00:37:40,930 --> 00:37:41,930
Then...

430
00:37:42,450 --> 00:37:44,120
Let us sleep in each other's arms.

431
00:38:02,740 --> 00:38:04,740
I wish we could cherish this moment
every day and night.

432
00:38:05,830 --> 00:38:08,040
I do not wish us
to be torn apart ever again.

433
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:16,700
I believe my father's heart has softened.

434
00:38:18,130 --> 00:38:19,640
So, you may rest easy now.

435
00:38:24,200 --> 00:38:25,640
Do you recall

436
00:38:26,170 --> 00:38:27,930
that time when you fell ill?

437
00:38:29,930 --> 00:38:31,590
I came in and sponged you down.

438
00:38:34,750 --> 00:38:35,750
I do.

439
00:38:36,240 --> 00:38:37,370
Chuay told me about it.

440
00:38:39,210 --> 00:38:41,340
You lapsed into delirium from the fever,

441
00:38:42,230 --> 00:38:43,850
saying in your sleep that
you wished to go home.

442
00:38:44,700 --> 00:38:46,440
I whispered something

443
00:38:47,420 --> 00:38:48,380
to you,

444
00:38:49,570 --> 00:38:51,120
though I believed
you could not remember it.

445
00:38:53,110 --> 00:38:54,930
So, I shall say it again now.

446
00:39:00,740 --> 00:39:03,400
Even if my father forbids your staying here,

447
00:39:05,160 --> 00:39:06,720
I shall follow.

448
00:39:09,090 --> 00:39:11,160
Wherever we may find ourselves,

449
00:39:13,650 --> 00:39:15,350
I shall be your home.

450
00:39:41,460 --> 00:39:42,460
What are you doing?

451
00:39:43,860 --> 00:39:44,700
The tip of the roof.

452
00:39:45,010 --> 00:39:46,780
You are my home, are you not?

453
00:39:51,270 --> 00:39:52,440
Let me feel your tip, will you?

454
00:39:52,940 --> 00:39:54,790
Can I feel it tonight?

455
00:39:55,230 --> 00:39:56,440
Stop it. Stop.

456
00:40:06,950 --> 00:40:08,020
Stop it, Phop!

457
00:40:08,580 --> 00:40:09,700
Let go of me!

458
00:40:12,530 --> 00:40:14,840
- Let me feel it, then.
- No.

459
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:18,140
- If your father hears us...
- No.

460
00:40:18,210 --> 00:40:19,640
Hey, stop it already.

461
00:40:44,710 --> 00:40:46,680
Master, I beg of you, tell me.

462
00:40:46,900 --> 00:40:48,880
I shall buy out all the tea
in this teahouse,

463
00:40:48,900 --> 00:40:49,840
every last pot of it.

464
00:40:50,490 --> 00:40:51,660
Every last pot of it, did you say?

465
00:40:53,080 --> 00:40:53,760
Good.

466
00:40:53,970 --> 00:40:57,590
A promise made is a promise kept.

467
00:41:01,320 --> 00:41:03,880
The Chinese man whom Pim accompanied

468
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:05,920
holds a position in Krom Tha Sai.

469
00:41:08,200 --> 00:41:10,550
Krom Tha Sai is responsible
for overseeing the Chinese,

470
00:41:10,630 --> 00:41:12,760
Vietnamese, and Japanese communities
in the capital,

471
00:41:12,910 --> 00:41:16,200
as well as managing royal junks
engaged in trade with those lands,

472
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:17,280
though chiefly the Chinese.

473
00:41:18,950 --> 00:41:19,960
If such is the case,

474
00:41:20,280 --> 00:41:21,700
it would come as no surprise

475
00:41:22,500 --> 00:41:24,640
if someone had forged my father's signature

476
00:41:24,730 --> 00:41:27,580
to permit those Chinese junks carrying opium

477
00:41:27,600 --> 00:41:29,000
to sail into our lands.

478
00:41:32,110 --> 00:41:34,080
Who might that Chinese man be?

479
00:41:34,620 --> 00:41:36,920
I am not certain of his identity.

480
00:41:37,150 --> 00:41:40,400
But Pim is the most beautiful lady

481
00:41:40,810 --> 00:41:43,990
in the Pavilion of Affection.

482
00:41:44,710 --> 00:41:47,200
She caters to the elite,

483
00:41:47,390 --> 00:41:49,320
and that Chinese man must therefore

484
00:41:49,540 --> 00:41:52,490
be a person of considerable influence.

485
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:54,560
If so,

486
00:41:55,270 --> 00:41:56,880
we must seek him out at the Royal Treasury.

487
00:41:58,130 --> 00:41:58,790
Where might it be?

488
00:41:58,820 --> 00:41:59,880
Pray, take me there, Phop.

489
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:01,460
Oh, oh, oh?

490
00:42:01,530 --> 00:42:03,570
Why leave?

491
00:42:03,610 --> 00:42:05,100
We are already here.

492
00:42:05,640 --> 00:42:07,310
- Right on cue.
- Unhand me.

493
00:42:07,350 --> 00:42:08,440
Draw him closer

494
00:42:08,470 --> 00:42:10,280
- and hold him tight.
- What?

495
00:42:10,750 --> 00:42:13,040
Finger of grace.

496
00:42:13,770 --> 00:42:14,680
Do not harm me!

497
00:42:29,750 --> 00:42:30,750
Master.

498
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:32,100
Thong.

499
00:42:32,350 --> 00:42:34,200
Pray, cease this.

500
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:38,780
Was it you

501
00:42:39,730 --> 00:42:42,160
who conspired with the man
who framed my father?!

502
00:42:42,580 --> 00:42:43,360
Unhand me.

503
00:42:44,190 --> 00:42:45,600
I do not know you.

504
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,500
It is only that

505
00:42:46,530 --> 00:42:49,210
I fear the violence
you have inflicted upon me in the past.

506
00:42:49,890 --> 00:42:51,800
Do you know Lord Preechapiban?

507
00:42:51,850 --> 00:42:54,080
Lord Preecha...

508
00:42:54,840 --> 00:42:55,920
piban...

509
00:42:58,240 --> 00:42:59,000
Who might that be?

510
00:43:03,110 --> 00:43:06,440
You once signed the warrant
that allowed those junks

511
00:43:07,060 --> 00:43:09,340
to pass through the river's mouth
without being searched,

512
00:43:09,360 --> 00:43:10,200
did you not?!

513
00:43:10,330 --> 00:43:11,220
I...

514
00:43:11,410 --> 00:43:12,240
I...

515
00:43:13,080 --> 00:43:14,820
Uh, the man who signed it

516
00:43:15,300 --> 00:43:17,930
was the father of my relative,

517
00:43:17,960 --> 00:43:20,070
a man to whom I owe filial respect as...

518
00:43:20,100 --> 00:43:20,780
Enough!

519
00:43:22,110 --> 00:43:23,110
Unhand him, Klao.

520
00:43:23,940 --> 00:43:25,640
The person who signed it

521
00:43:26,140 --> 00:43:28,600
must be a high-ranking official,

522
00:43:29,620 --> 00:43:31,580
likely older than this man.

523
00:43:36,080 --> 00:43:37,160
What a sheer waste of time this is.

524
00:43:40,780 --> 00:43:42,460
It would be easier to hunt down the forger

525
00:43:42,480 --> 00:43:45,200
than to find the truth in the Port Department.

526
00:43:46,400 --> 00:43:49,040
It seems you must return to
the Pavilion of Affection

527
00:43:49,530 --> 00:43:51,820
and draw the truth from Pim.

528
00:43:53,390 --> 00:43:54,960
This is our only path forward.

529
00:43:59,120 --> 00:44:01,050
But Pim would likely flee from me.

530
00:44:02,150 --> 00:44:05,340
Asking you and Chuay to wear other disguises

531
00:44:05,830 --> 00:44:07,100
may no longer suffice.

532
00:44:13,420 --> 00:44:14,340
Chuay.

533
00:44:15,360 --> 00:44:17,000
We need a helping hand.

534
00:44:18,090 --> 00:44:19,080
My Lord,

535
00:44:19,250 --> 00:44:20,840
what would you have me do this time?

536
00:44:20,890 --> 00:44:22,800
I am too afraid to wear
a woman's disguise again.

537
00:44:23,330 --> 00:44:24,240
That is not what I meant.

538
00:44:24,860 --> 00:44:27,040
Summon the physician and Kaew to me.

539
00:44:49,480 --> 00:44:51,760
Jom, cease your pursuit of me.

540
00:44:51,840 --> 00:44:52,840
It is most irritating.

541
00:44:53,020 --> 00:44:54,160
I am here to select my fabrics.

542
00:44:54,290 --> 00:44:55,550
Well, I am here to assist you.

543
00:45:02,240 --> 00:45:03,540
- You are after this one.
- Would you like this one?

544
00:45:05,480 --> 00:45:06,280
Uh...

545
00:45:12,420 --> 00:45:13,440
I shall take this one.

546
00:45:13,560 --> 00:45:14,280
Certainly.

547
00:45:24,770 --> 00:45:26,550
That is the son of High Lord Sintaranurak.

548
00:45:27,000 --> 00:45:28,300
It is said that he is effeminate,

549
00:45:31,980 --> 00:45:33,540
and it would appear to be true.

550
00:45:34,240 --> 00:45:36,280
He seems to be procuring an item
for a lady's use as well.

551
00:45:36,860 --> 00:45:37,760
How peculiar.

552
00:45:43,720 --> 00:45:44,800
Jom.

553
00:45:46,080 --> 00:45:47,040
Let us leave.

554
00:45:47,840 --> 00:45:49,600
It is you who are peculiar.

555
00:45:51,590 --> 00:45:54,360
What kind of gentleman speaks ill of others
without a hint of shame?

556
00:45:56,260 --> 00:45:58,000
Kaew has done no wrong.

557
00:45:58,630 --> 00:46:00,480
He merely finds pleasure
in things that differ from others.

558
00:46:00,950 --> 00:46:02,030
Look at how you protect one another.

559
00:46:03,680 --> 00:46:05,280
One might think you are husband and wife.

560
00:46:05,400 --> 00:46:06,760
Or is it merely a passing fancy?

561
00:46:42,260 --> 00:46:42,990
And so?!!

562
00:46:43,440 --> 00:46:45,480
Try and find a soul of such grace
as my spouse if you can.

563
00:47:16,520 --> 00:47:17,520
Thank you.

564
00:47:26,950 --> 00:47:28,830
You have my deepest gratitude

565
00:47:29,290 --> 00:47:30,680
for protecting me.

566
00:47:32,210 --> 00:47:34,160
But calling me your spouse...

567
00:47:36,300 --> 00:47:37,630
Do not address me in such a manner.

568
00:47:38,530 --> 00:47:39,530
It is not to my liking.

569
00:47:40,910 --> 00:47:41,840
Forgive me.

570
00:47:43,220 --> 00:47:45,000
- I thought...
- Never again.

571
00:47:48,110 --> 00:47:48,840
Because...

572
00:47:50,670 --> 00:47:51,950
you have never asked.

573
00:47:54,930 --> 00:47:55,930
If that is so,

574
00:47:56,300 --> 00:47:58,000
I shall ask you this very instant.

575
00:48:02,100 --> 00:48:03,520
Jom.

576
00:48:05,050 --> 00:48:06,760
Why do you...

577
00:48:10,300 --> 00:48:12,100
In your absence,

578
00:48:12,480 --> 00:48:13,760
I feel as though

579
00:48:14,420 --> 00:48:17,680
the other half of my very soul has vanished.

580
00:48:19,190 --> 00:48:21,010
Without you by my side to assist me,

581
00:48:22,010 --> 00:48:23,360
to offer your support,

582
00:48:24,240 --> 00:48:25,880
your affection and care,

583
00:48:27,870 --> 00:48:29,670
and to see to my needs,

584
00:48:32,920 --> 00:48:35,560
it is far worse than any slander
I have endured.

585
00:48:43,000 --> 00:48:44,040
I sincerely apologize

586
00:48:45,680 --> 00:48:47,480
for not realizing it sooner.

587
00:48:50,480 --> 00:48:53,100
I am now ready to tell you

588
00:48:54,430 --> 00:48:57,540
whom I wish you to be in my life.

589
00:49:05,810 --> 00:49:07,320
Allow me to care for you

590
00:49:07,400 --> 00:49:09,920
as my dearest beloved, Kaew.

591
00:49:23,010 --> 00:49:28,870
♫I simply wish to cherish your gaze forever♫

592
00:49:28,940 --> 00:49:34,450
♫I wish to forever hold your hands,
it has never felt better♫

593
00:49:34,480 --> 00:49:43,620
♫I never thought
I'd hear these words from you ever♫

594
00:49:44,220 --> 00:49:48,700
♫I once gave up♫

595
00:49:48,740 --> 00:49:54,340
♫Your coldness did me in, and I could not last♫

596
00:49:54,370 --> 00:49:59,870
♫But simply seeing you right here,♫

597
00:49:59,910 --> 00:50:05,450
♫It's too much to hold back my tears♫

598
00:50:07,280 --> 00:50:08,120
I shall allow it,

599
00:50:08,390 --> 00:50:09,600
Jom, my beloved.

600
00:50:15,710 --> 00:50:21,240
♫I'm willing to give you all my heart♫

601
00:50:21,590 --> 00:50:26,790
♫I give it willingly, like never before♫

602
00:50:27,150 --> 00:50:31,290
♫Thank you for turning back to me,♫

603
00:50:31,330 --> 00:50:33,780
♫And listening to your heart's own needs♫

604
00:50:33,830 --> 00:50:42,520
♫It brings me joy to stand right here with you♫

605
00:50:46,450 --> 00:50:50,480
♫And I love you most of all,♫

606
00:50:55,410 --> 00:50:59,400
♫My dear♫

607
00:50:59,860 --> 00:51:00,840
Physician!

608
00:51:01,460 --> 00:51:02,460
Master Kaew!

609
00:51:16,300 --> 00:51:18,600
I had to venture from Master Jom's

610
00:51:19,400 --> 00:51:20,480
to Master Kaew's manor

611
00:51:21,110 --> 00:51:23,020
and the canal market.

612
00:51:27,920 --> 00:51:30,380
You wish for us to escort you into...

613
00:51:32,450 --> 00:51:33,980
the House of Pleasure?

614
00:51:35,640 --> 00:51:36,440
Yes.

615
00:51:36,970 --> 00:51:39,100
Tonight is the fifteenth night
of the waning moon.

616
00:51:39,520 --> 00:51:42,760
Cherd should smuggle opium tonight, if true.

617
00:51:44,450 --> 00:51:45,880
Your task is

618
00:51:46,210 --> 00:51:48,880
to uncover exactly
which temple that hut lies behind.

619
00:51:49,480 --> 00:51:51,240
Through the House of Pleasure?

620
00:51:53,960 --> 00:51:55,700
Through the House of Pleasure.

621
00:51:56,260 --> 00:51:58,960
That is because Pim,
a lady at the House of Pleasure,

622
00:51:59,130 --> 00:52:00,510
may very well be privy to the truth.

623
00:52:00,590 --> 00:52:02,200
Did you pay any heed to his words at all,

624
00:52:03,060 --> 00:52:05,180
or was your mind
wholly fixed on that one thing?

625
00:52:08,670 --> 00:52:09,700
As for Phop,

626
00:52:09,720 --> 00:52:11,580
dispatch the patrol
to reinforce the position

627
00:52:11,950 --> 00:52:13,440
once the temple has been identified.

628
00:52:13,790 --> 00:52:14,480
Yes.

629
00:52:15,200 --> 00:52:16,680
I must make haste and depart.

630
00:52:16,920 --> 00:52:19,680
Klao, lay out our course of action
to Kaew and Jom.

631
00:52:25,760 --> 00:52:28,160
Keep yourself safe, my dearest.

632
00:52:32,960 --> 00:52:33,620
Understood.

633
00:52:34,900 --> 00:52:36,960
Once this night is over,

634
00:52:38,070 --> 00:52:40,410
we shall at last live in peace.

635
00:52:41,350 --> 00:52:43,300
Once this night is over,

636
00:52:43,780 --> 00:52:45,800
I shall ask my father
for your hand in marriage.

637
00:53:06,910 --> 00:53:08,720
You are right-handed, are you not?

638
00:53:09,500 --> 00:53:11,360
Why, then, do you bear your sword
in your left hand?

639
00:53:12,940 --> 00:53:14,880
One must keep the dominant hand free,

640
00:53:15,740 --> 00:53:17,560
so that the sword
may be drawn in this manner.

641
00:53:22,340 --> 00:53:23,240
Why the question?

642
00:53:23,930 --> 00:53:26,210
It vaguely came to me that

643
00:53:26,390 --> 00:53:28,780
the official who visited my father in Phichit

644
00:53:31,440 --> 00:53:32,880
carried his sword in his right hand.

645
00:53:34,040 --> 00:53:35,080
That would imply that

646
00:53:36,110 --> 00:53:37,550
he is left-handed, would he not?

647
00:53:45,000 --> 00:53:46,440
My deepest thanks to you.

648
00:53:47,250 --> 00:53:48,230
I now see clearly...

649
00:53:48,260 --> 00:53:50,610
how I must proceed with this investigation.

650
00:53:53,520 --> 00:53:54,620
I shall take my leave now.

651
00:53:55,820 --> 00:53:58,000
Once the truth is discovered,
make haste to my department.

652
00:54:22,330 --> 00:54:22,960
Now, then...

653
00:54:24,740 --> 00:54:25,920
Our plan

654
00:54:26,630 --> 00:54:27,760
is as follows.

655
00:54:29,810 --> 00:54:31,440
Pim has been shunning me,

656
00:54:31,880 --> 00:54:34,200
yet I must speak with her.

657
00:54:35,890 --> 00:54:38,360
One of us must wear a disguise
and call for her.

658
00:54:49,450 --> 00:54:50,020
Me!

659
00:54:50,630 --> 00:54:52,880
I shall take upon myself this daunting task.

660
00:54:53,070 --> 00:54:54,560
You certainly seem quite eager, Jom.

661
00:54:59,030 --> 00:55:00,080
We

662
00:55:00,660 --> 00:55:03,520
will need Jom for our backup plan.

663
00:55:04,450 --> 00:55:05,490
So...

664
00:55:06,020 --> 00:55:09,400
The one who assumes the guise shall be...

665
00:55:13,650 --> 00:55:16,040
I am here to officially inspect
the House of Pleasure!

666
00:55:18,730 --> 00:55:20,400
Inspect this establishment, I hear?

667
00:55:23,440 --> 00:55:26,000
We have paid our dues

668
00:55:26,690 --> 00:55:28,040
and tributes

669
00:55:28,260 --> 00:55:30,000
to the authorities without fail.

670
00:55:32,710 --> 00:55:34,800
Do not be shy, Master.

671
00:55:35,200 --> 00:55:36,690
If it is pleasure you seek,

672
00:55:36,780 --> 00:55:38,520
then speak your mind plainly.

673
00:55:38,900 --> 00:55:41,880
I shall offer you my service.

674
00:55:48,540 --> 00:55:49,200
Uh...

675
00:55:52,530 --> 00:55:53,640
Is Pim within the establishment?

676
00:55:54,930 --> 00:55:56,850
She is not here.

677
00:56:00,510 --> 00:56:02,960
I, Puang, shall take her stead.

678
00:56:03,100 --> 00:56:04,680
Compelling, is she not?

679
00:56:09,500 --> 00:56:10,580
If that is the case,

680
00:56:11,150 --> 00:56:12,560
then I shall take my leave.

681
00:56:13,150 --> 00:56:14,720
What if Kaew's ruse were to falter?

682
00:56:15,390 --> 00:56:16,110
Deary me...

683
00:56:16,140 --> 00:56:18,080
you have indeed
placed your trust in me, Jom.

684
00:56:21,120 --> 00:56:22,200
I simply...

685
00:56:23,620 --> 00:56:26,000
I am merely devising another plan, my Kaew.

686
00:56:29,890 --> 00:56:31,000
This is beyond me.

687
00:56:45,000 --> 00:56:45,730
I...

688
00:56:50,900 --> 00:56:52,040
I am here to see Pim.

689
00:57:00,010 --> 00:57:02,000
She is not here.

690
00:57:04,280 --> 00:57:06,480
I, Puang, shall take her stead.

691
00:57:08,200 --> 00:57:09,780
Allow us

692
00:57:09,950 --> 00:57:12,440
to satisfy you, Master.

693
00:57:28,800 --> 00:57:30,600
I cannot do it!

694
00:57:31,910 --> 00:57:33,510
I simply cannot!

695
00:57:35,400 --> 00:57:37,110
I cannot do this.

696
00:57:37,360 --> 00:57:38,960
I cannot!

697
00:57:47,310 --> 00:57:49,080
Even Jom has failed.

698
00:57:50,920 --> 00:57:51,920
Now, then,

699
00:57:52,650 --> 00:57:55,920
the time has come for my ultimate gambit.

700
00:57:56,120 --> 00:57:57,440
- Your ultimate gambit?
- Your ultimate gambit?

701
00:57:57,950 --> 00:57:58,720
Yes!

702
00:57:59,010 --> 00:58:01,080
It shall go as follows.

703
00:58:01,360 --> 00:58:02,240
Help!

704
00:58:04,850 --> 00:58:06,200
I have been bitten by a serpent!!

705
00:58:09,730 --> 00:58:10,620
Ouch!

706
00:58:11,070 --> 00:58:11,920
Ow!

707
00:58:14,150 --> 00:58:15,090
Ouch!

708
00:58:18,420 --> 00:58:20,800
Ow!

709
00:58:25,000 --> 00:58:26,980
A serpent took hold of him.

710
00:58:31,920 --> 00:58:33,000
Good heavens!

711
00:58:33,250 --> 00:58:34,240
Good Ladies,

712
00:58:34,520 --> 00:58:36,280
kindly bring
a physician to treat him, would you?

713
00:58:42,960 --> 00:58:44,480
Where were you bitten?

714
00:58:44,740 --> 00:58:46,330
- Shall we search for the bite mark?
- I see nothing.

715
00:58:47,260 --> 00:58:48,440
A serpent of what kind?

716
00:58:49,160 --> 00:58:49,540
I could not see...

717
00:58:49,580 --> 00:58:51,360
I shall draw the venom out myself!

718
00:58:51,420 --> 00:58:52,920
I shall take on the task as well.

719
00:58:53,020 --> 00:58:54,710
- Where is it?
- I can find it nowhere.

720
00:58:54,750 --> 00:58:55,370
Where is the bite mark?

721
00:58:55,400 --> 00:58:56,600
- Pray, tell.
- Is it up here?

722
00:58:56,690 --> 00:58:57,390
I can find it nowhere.

723
00:58:57,840 --> 00:59:00,010
- It is not down here.
- No bite mark to be found here.

724
00:59:00,040 --> 00:59:01,440
What kind of serpent bit you?

725
00:59:02,220 --> 00:59:03,640
I have yet to find one.

726
00:59:04,890 --> 00:59:06,530
I, too, shall draw out the venom!

727
00:59:06,560 --> 00:59:08,210
It is better for me to take on the task.

728
00:59:08,230 --> 00:59:09,680
- Where?
- Here, is it not?

729
00:59:10,100 --> 00:59:13,000
- There, is it?
- Oh, allow me to do it as well.

730
00:59:13,030 --> 00:59:13,740
Ow!

731
00:59:13,770 --> 00:59:15,340
Pray, loosen your garments.

732
00:59:15,540 --> 00:59:16,800
Did it bite you in the arm?

733
00:59:17,130 --> 00:59:18,120
Your arm, is it not?

734
00:59:18,890 --> 00:59:20,020
Or is it your leg that it bit?

735
00:59:20,050 --> 00:59:21,130
His leg...

736
00:59:21,150 --> 00:59:22,300
- His arm...
- Is it here?

737
00:59:23,850 --> 00:59:24,590
Curses!

738
00:59:24,750 --> 00:59:27,780
Can I not have a single night of peace
in my own establishment?

739
00:59:30,080 --> 00:59:32,600
- Oh, make way!
- She is coming.

740
00:59:32,740 --> 00:59:35,160
What is all this commotion?!

741
00:59:39,380 --> 00:59:40,260
Physician Jom?

742
00:59:44,550 --> 00:59:45,680
Kaew?

743
00:59:45,970 --> 00:59:47,400
The son of High Lord Sintaranurak?

744
00:59:49,220 --> 00:59:50,920
What brought both of you here?

745
01:00:00,950 --> 01:00:01,680
Pim!

746
01:00:05,800 --> 01:00:07,120
You said we are friends, did you not?

747
01:00:08,130 --> 01:00:09,680
Why, then, do you avert your face from me?

748
01:00:43,080 --> 01:00:45,030
It is best for you
to stay away from me, Klao.

749
01:00:45,920 --> 01:00:47,440
Cease this charade of illness.

750
01:00:48,940 --> 01:00:50,280
Speak truthfully,

751
01:00:51,370 --> 01:00:53,120
and tell me why you shun me.

752
01:00:54,880 --> 01:00:55,800
Is Cherd the reason?

753
01:00:56,540 --> 01:00:57,520
What did he do to you?

754
01:01:01,580 --> 01:01:03,360
He is consumed with jealousy.

755
01:01:05,500 --> 01:01:07,280
He has forbidden me from coming near you.

756
01:01:10,730 --> 01:01:13,100
Should I disobey, he shall have me killed!

757
01:01:20,120 --> 01:01:22,360
I beg you, have some compassion
for my situation.

758
01:01:27,060 --> 01:01:29,600
Leave this establishment, I pray.

759
01:01:35,110 --> 01:01:35,790
Pim.

760
01:01:48,560 --> 01:01:49,800
You cry

761
01:01:50,430 --> 01:01:51,900
because you are afraid, do you not?

762
01:01:54,400 --> 01:01:55,440
Or perhaps you believe...

763
01:01:57,250 --> 01:01:59,520
you were the cause
of my previous disappearance?

764
01:02:05,540 --> 01:02:07,240
The night we last met,

765
01:02:10,300 --> 01:02:11,780
I did ask you

766
01:02:13,110 --> 01:02:14,800
for the location
of the meeting place, did I not?

767
01:02:19,780 --> 01:02:21,040
Klao...

768
01:02:24,190 --> 01:02:26,160
Have your memories returned?

769
01:02:33,010 --> 01:02:33,650
Yes.

770
01:02:36,130 --> 01:02:36,870
At present,

771
01:02:37,620 --> 01:02:40,280
Phop and I are investigating this matter.

772
01:02:44,010 --> 01:02:45,490
It all comes back to me now.

773
01:02:47,220 --> 01:02:50,160
There is no point in lying
or hiding from me any further.

774
01:02:55,140 --> 01:02:56,700
Simply give me the answer

775
01:02:58,050 --> 01:02:59,800
and I shall no longer set foot here again.

776
01:03:03,170 --> 01:03:06,560
That abandoned hut by the pond
near the temple,

777
01:03:09,000 --> 01:03:10,160
to which temple does it belong?

778
01:03:21,490 --> 01:03:22,560
Is Kla not here?

779
01:03:24,850 --> 01:03:25,710
He is not.

780
01:03:25,990 --> 01:03:28,240
He has been keeping a close eye
on Cherd, my Lord.

781
01:03:29,720 --> 01:03:30,720
Leave, all of you.

782
01:03:45,500 --> 01:03:49,160
Wat Sema Thong is the first temple
we shall come across as we sail along the river.

783
01:03:49,800 --> 01:03:51,880
However, if we go ashore from Sam Khok,

784
01:03:52,940 --> 01:03:56,440
where we have seized opium
on several occasions,

785
01:03:56,760 --> 01:03:58,280
it would instead be Wat Sema Khu.

786
01:04:03,320 --> 01:04:04,000
Lord Phop,

787
01:04:05,600 --> 01:04:08,260
can you not yet put your doubts
about that hut behind the temple to rest?

788
01:04:12,060 --> 01:04:13,440
I simply cannot.

789
01:04:14,060 --> 01:04:16,860
Wat Sema Khu
lies close to the canal market,

790
01:04:17,760 --> 01:04:18,840
which falls within Cherd's territory.

791
01:04:20,080 --> 01:04:21,920
It lies also within...

792
01:04:22,180 --> 01:04:24,610
your and your father's jurisdiction.

793
01:04:30,810 --> 01:04:31,680
Lord Phop.

794
01:04:33,400 --> 01:04:34,680
Are you suspicious of me?

795
01:04:40,350 --> 01:04:41,640
Certainly not, Lord Harn.

796
01:04:44,490 --> 01:04:45,960
My suspicion lies with your father.

797
01:04:49,490 --> 01:04:50,320
Impossible.

798
01:04:51,800 --> 01:04:53,440
How would my father do such a thing?

799
01:04:53,810 --> 01:04:55,100
I have reasons to believe,

800
01:04:56,160 --> 01:04:57,720
but time is of the essence.

801
01:04:58,810 --> 01:04:59,760
Lord Harn,

802
01:05:00,440 --> 01:05:02,280
you have the power to set wrongs aright.

803
01:05:03,680 --> 01:05:05,920
At this hour,
I have no one else to rely on but you.

804
01:05:08,490 --> 01:05:09,850
Should your father be guiltless,

805
01:05:11,040 --> 01:05:12,290
then take it

806
01:05:13,140 --> 01:05:14,940
as my own misunderstanding.

807
01:05:23,340 --> 01:05:24,340
If such is the case,

808
01:05:27,110 --> 01:05:28,510
what would you have me do?

809
01:05:45,900 --> 01:05:46,860
Pim.

810
01:05:47,320 --> 01:05:49,030
No need for such formalities between us.

811
01:05:57,530 --> 01:06:00,320
Let me serve you with all my heart.

812
01:06:04,320 --> 01:06:05,690
And I beg of you...

813
01:06:06,940 --> 01:06:08,670
never return to this place again

814
01:06:09,990 --> 01:06:12,360
lest you invite disaster upon yourself.

815
01:06:18,320 --> 01:06:19,560
What is the meaning of that?

816
01:06:20,330 --> 01:06:22,480
But that hut...

817
01:06:23,330 --> 01:06:25,200
It is the meeting place, is it not?

818
01:06:27,640 --> 01:06:28,640
Indeed it is.

819
01:06:32,140 --> 01:06:34,780
It is a staging ground
for opium smuggled from Sam Khok,

820
01:06:37,000 --> 01:06:39,040
bound for the capital.

821
01:06:39,610 --> 01:06:40,280
And...

822
01:06:41,010 --> 01:06:41,900
So...

823
01:06:43,030 --> 01:06:44,200
Which temple is it?

824
01:06:45,400 --> 01:06:46,400
Is it Wat Sema Muang,

825
01:06:47,140 --> 01:06:48,140
Wat Sema Khu,

826
01:06:48,510 --> 01:06:49,560
or Wat Sema Thong?

827
01:06:51,800 --> 01:06:53,720
It is Wat Sema Muang.

828
01:07:01,520 --> 01:07:04,000
My heart is burdened with guilt.

829
01:07:05,820 --> 01:07:08,200
The last time I spoke thus,

830
01:07:09,630 --> 01:07:11,140
rumors reached my ears...

831
01:07:12,020 --> 01:07:13,800
that you had perished.

832
01:07:14,890 --> 01:07:18,740
I have tormented myself
in every waking moment,

833
01:07:19,810 --> 01:07:23,600
believing I was the cause of your demise.

834
01:07:32,480 --> 01:07:33,430
No wonder

835
01:07:34,920 --> 01:07:36,820
you wept...

836
01:07:41,310 --> 01:07:42,680
when we first met again.

837
01:07:47,490 --> 01:07:49,430
You have my deepest gratitude, Pim.

838
01:07:52,850 --> 01:07:54,080
What you have done is right.

839
01:07:55,990 --> 01:07:57,590
I shall leave this place at once

840
01:07:59,290 --> 01:08:00,610
and never return.

841
01:08:05,600 --> 01:08:07,300
I shall not cause you trouble again.

842
01:08:12,500 --> 01:08:13,160
But...

843
01:08:13,800 --> 01:08:15,620
if you still hold on to me thus,

844
01:08:17,600 --> 01:08:19,250
how then could I rise and leave?

845
01:08:25,740 --> 01:08:29,700
Grant me your forgiveness,
I beg of you, Klao.

846
01:08:31,520 --> 01:08:32,640
My forgiveness...

847
01:09:00,520 --> 01:09:01,399
Master.

848
01:09:01,490 --> 01:09:03,319
Calm yourself, A-Chai.

849
01:09:10,800 --> 01:09:12,520
You need not trouble yourself

850
01:09:12,899 --> 01:09:14,319
to serve me a cup of tea, High Lord.

851
01:09:16,010 --> 01:09:17,840
Allow me to serve you.

852
01:09:32,880 --> 01:09:35,479
You have gone to great lengths
to summon me here.

853
01:09:36,500 --> 01:09:37,680
What is the matter?

854
01:09:38,609 --> 01:09:39,960
Is it something pleasant?

855
01:09:44,760 --> 01:09:46,040
Indeed it is.

856
01:09:49,399 --> 01:09:50,359
At last,

857
01:09:51,399 --> 01:09:53,120
the truth has come to light.

858
01:09:58,340 --> 01:09:59,640
The truth?

859
01:10:00,660 --> 01:10:03,420
Is it regarding
Phop declining his own marriage?

860
01:10:04,190 --> 01:10:05,000
No.

861
01:10:05,430 --> 01:10:06,300
It is not so.

862
01:10:07,030 --> 01:10:08,510
What has come to light is that

863
01:10:09,650 --> 01:10:12,200
you framed Lord Preechapiban,

864
01:10:14,320 --> 01:10:16,320
permitting the junks carrying opium

865
01:10:18,330 --> 01:10:22,270
to sail into the river's mouth
without being searched.

866
01:10:23,120 --> 01:10:26,320
Oh, compose yourself
and speak at a steady pace.

867
01:10:26,720 --> 01:10:29,400
You shall be out of breath
if you continue thus.

868
01:10:32,230 --> 01:10:33,440
Now then...

869
01:10:34,330 --> 01:10:35,330
Was it you

870
01:10:37,280 --> 01:10:40,310
who orchestrated all of this?

871
01:10:53,420 --> 01:10:54,100
Indeed.

872
01:10:57,420 --> 01:10:59,400
And what exactly do you think you can do?

873
01:11:03,800 --> 01:11:04,920
Master.

874
01:11:05,930 --> 01:11:07,520
Are you certain this is the way

875
01:11:08,190 --> 01:11:10,400
that leads to your father's stash?

876
01:11:12,300 --> 01:11:13,240
Assuredly.

877
01:11:13,830 --> 01:11:16,300
He has been visiting Wat Sema Khu
more often of late.

878
01:11:16,900 --> 01:11:18,180
Thus, this must be the place.

879
01:11:22,210 --> 01:11:23,400
Make haste.

880
01:11:23,740 --> 01:11:24,920
Judging by how long we have been here,

881
01:11:24,950 --> 01:11:26,610
I am certain it has almost passed
the second period.

882
01:11:40,400 --> 01:11:41,160
Lord Harn.

883
01:11:42,130 --> 01:11:44,600
Does the hut you spoke of truly exist?

884
01:11:46,430 --> 01:11:47,240
It ought to.

885
01:11:48,320 --> 01:11:50,000
I am certain I have seen it.

886
01:11:51,520 --> 01:11:54,260
Or has my father caught wind of us
and had it demolished beforehand?

887
01:11:56,260 --> 01:11:58,780
How could an entire hut
vanish without a trace?

888
01:12:07,390 --> 01:12:09,200
Either that, or you have deceived me.

889
01:12:13,230 --> 01:12:15,200
Cease this charade, Lord Harn.

890
01:12:16,200 --> 01:12:17,960
I know full well you are behind this.

891
01:12:25,590 --> 01:12:27,280
If you already do,

892
01:12:28,740 --> 01:12:30,440
why then did you choose to follow me here?

893
01:12:34,610 --> 01:12:36,190
Because I still have hope

894
01:12:37,490 --> 01:12:39,200
that a patrolman like you

895
01:12:40,000 --> 01:12:42,110
would not commit such a misdeed.

896
01:12:52,720 --> 01:12:53,800
If such is the case,

897
01:12:56,390 --> 01:13:00,000
do pray that
you make it out alive in one piece,

898
01:13:00,630 --> 01:13:01,550
Lord Phop.

899
01:13:16,390 --> 01:13:17,880
What is it you are saying?

900
01:13:18,830 --> 01:13:20,080
In the previous incident,

901
01:13:23,010 --> 01:13:24,220
you were not in the wrong.

902
01:13:26,230 --> 01:13:27,400
Indeed.

903
01:13:30,900 --> 01:13:32,460
But this time,

904
01:13:34,840 --> 01:13:37,120
it is certain that I am.

905
01:14:34,080 --> 01:14:34,890
There is a traitor among Phop’s men.

906
01:14:34,930 --> 01:14:36,880
Kaew, summon the patrols here at once.

907
01:14:36,940 --> 01:14:38,040
I cannot do this.

908
01:14:40,560 --> 01:14:41,680
I place full trust in you.

909
01:14:41,990 --> 01:14:44,880
Never have I known a soul
so wise and resilient as you.

910
01:14:48,120 --> 01:14:49,560
Fear not

911
01:14:49,580 --> 01:14:51,160
that you will be alone in hell,

912
01:14:51,530 --> 01:14:53,320
for your good brother

913
01:14:53,840 --> 01:14:55,920
shall soon join you.

914
01:15:01,620 --> 01:15:04,400
I call upon the Buddha as my witness:

915
01:15:04,790 --> 01:15:07,090
my heart belongs to you alone,
and ever shall it remain.

916
01:15:07,600 --> 01:15:08,960
After this day,

917
01:15:09,420 --> 01:15:10,870
if I am gone,

918
01:15:11,840 --> 01:15:13,500
promise me you will live well.

919
01:15:13,800 --> 01:15:19,540
♫I'm willing to give you all my heart♫

920
01:15:19,590 --> 01:15:25,190
♫I give it willingly, like never before♫

921
01:15:25,230 --> 01:15:29,080
♫Thank you for turning back to me,♫

922
01:15:29,380 --> 01:15:31,850
♫And listening to your heart's own needs♫

923
01:15:31,890 --> 01:15:40,720
♫It brings me joy to stand right here with you♫

924
01:16:01,210 --> 01:16:06,320
♫I'm so happy you dared to say we are in love♫

925
01:16:09,120 --> 01:16:13,120
[Love Upon a Time Series]
